@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_hlkyyr(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = wp.exp(0.36)
    v0 = 0.39
    tmp = (v0 + wp.abs(v0))
    v1 = ((wp.abs(v2 + 0.96) / wp.exp(v2 + 0.65)) * wp.cos(wp.sin(tmp + 0.48)))
    v2 = ((0.16 - 0.38) / wp.exp(wp.abs(tmp + 0.56)))
    tmp = 0.42
    v0 = (tmp * wp.abs(0.08))
    data[tid] = v0
